# Environment Configuration

This file contains all the environment variables needed for the Khisima frontend application.

## Required Variables

# Backend API Configuration
VITE_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000

## Optional Variables

# File Storage Configuration (Tigris/S3)
VITE_PUBLIC_S3_BUCKET_NAME_IMAGES=khisima-images

# Analytics and Monitoring
VITE_VERCEL_ANALYTICS_ID=your_analytics_id

# Feature Flags
VITE_ENABLE_AI_AGENT=true
VITE_ENABLE_DARK_MODE=true

## Development Environment

# For local development, use these values:
# VITE_APP_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000
# VITE_PUBLIC_S3_BUCKET_NAME_IMAGES=khisima-dev-images

## Production Environment

# For production deployment, update these values:
# VITE_APP_API_BASE_URL=https://api.khisima.com
# VITE_PUBLIC_S3_BUCKET_NAME_IMAGES=khisima-prod-images

## Notes

# - All variables must be prefixed with VITE_ to be accessible in the frontend
# - Restart the development server after changing environment variables
# - Never commit sensitive values to version control
# - Use different values for development, staging, and production environments